<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 03:13:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>荷兰银行将以 7.3 亿美元收购德国银行 Hauck Aufhäuser Lamp</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abn-amro-buy-german-lender-hauck-aufhuser-lampe-730-million-2024-05-28/</link><description>荷兰银行已同意以 6.72 亿欧元（7.3 亿美元）收购私人银行 Hauck Aufhäuser Lampe (HAL)，巩固其作为德国三大财富管理公司之一的地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 03:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abn-amro-buy-german-lender-hauck-aufhuser-lampe-730-million-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市反弹后漂移，华尔街重新开放成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-28/</link><description>继前一交易日上涨后，周二亚洲股市涨跌不一，因为在一些关键通胀数据公布之前，欧洲即将降息的押注增加，提振了风险偏好。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 02:24:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>韩国、美国、日本核特使谴责朝鲜发射卫星</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-japan-nuclear-envoys-condemn-north-korea-satellite-launch-2024-05-28/</link><description>首尔外交部表示，韩国、美国和日本的核特使在周二的电话中强烈谴责朝鲜最近发射卫星的企图。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 02:20:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-japan-nuclear-envoys-condemn-north-korea-satellite-launch-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>市场等待重要的全球通胀报告，美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-ebbs-markets-await-key-global-inflation-reports-2024-05-28/</link><description>风险偏好小幅回升后，美元周二下跌，但在本周主要经济体公布关键通胀数据之前，美元兑其他货币保持窄幅波动，市场正在寻求全球利率前景的指引。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 00:55:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-ebbs-markets-await-key-global-inflation-reports-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，诺基亚将向葡萄牙 MEO 供应 5G 无线电设备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-supply-5g-radio-equipment-portugals-meo-sources-say-2024-05-27/</link><description>据诺基亚内部博客文章和两位知情人士透露，诺基亚将赢得一份向葡萄牙电信运营商 MEO 供应 5G 无线电设备的合同。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-supply-5g-radio-equipment-portugals-meo-sources-say-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟通过法律增加国内绿色技术产量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/eu-clears-law-increase-domestic-green-tech-production-2024-05-27/</link><description>欧盟各国政府周一正式通过了一项新法律，旨在确保欧盟生产 40% 的太阳能电池板、风力涡轮机、热泵和其他清洁技术设备，并帮助欧洲工业与美国和中国竞争对手竞争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/eu-clears-law-increase-domestic-green-tech-production-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本警告居民躲避朝鲜导弹威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-warns-residents-take-cover-north-korean-missile-threat-2024-05-27/</link><description>日本政府周一向南部居民发出紧急警告，要求他们躲避朝鲜导弹的可能威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-warns-residents-take-cover-north-korean-missile-threat-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>据《环球时报》报道，中国工业界寻求对欧盟猪肉进口进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-industry-seek-probe-into-eu-pork-imports-global-times-reports-2024-05-27/</link><description>官方支持的《环球时报》周六援引一位不愿透露姓名的“业内人士”的话说，中国企业计划要求当局对从欧盟进口的部分猪肉产品展开反倾销调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-industry-seek-probe-into-eu-pork-imports-global-times-reports-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>标准普尔全球表示，中国的房地产刺激措施增加了中小城市银行的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-stimulus-raises-risks-banks-smaller-cities-sp-global-says-2024-05-27/</link><description>标准普尔全球周一表示，中国为重振陷入困境的房地产市场而采取的最新举措可能会给在低线城市运营的银行带来风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-stimulus-raises-risks-banks-smaller-cities-sp-global-says-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国将于5月28日至31日在黄海进行火箭发射</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conduct-rocket-launches-yellow-sea-may-28-31-2024-05-27/</link><description>据一份声明称，中国海事局表示将于5月28日至31日在黄海进行火箭发射。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:52:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conduct-rocket-launches-yellow-sea-may-28-31-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示巴西超越比利时成为中国电动车、混合动力车最大出口市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-surpasses-belgium-top-export-market-chinese-evs-hybrids-data-shows-2024-05-27/</link><description>行业数据显示，随着欧盟对中国电动汽车反补贴调查，中国汽车制造商增加了对非欧洲市场的销量，巴西已超过比利时成为中国新能源汽车最大出口市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-surpasses-belgium-top-export-market-chinese-evs-hybrids-data-shows-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜谴责首尔邻国峰会上的无核化呼吁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-condemns-denuclearisation-discussion-south-korea-japan-china-summit-2024-05-27/</link><description>朝鲜周一谴责中国、日本和韩国承诺实现朝鲜半岛无核化，称三国在首尔举行的罕见峰会后发表的联合声明是侵犯朝鲜主权的“严重政治挑衅”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 09:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-condemns-denuclearisation-discussion-south-korea-japan-china-summit-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>万科亏损底价出售深圳地块</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-sells-shenzhen-land-plot-loss-making-reserve-price-2024-05-27/</link><description>周一提交的一份文件显示，资金短缺的万科通过拍卖以人民币 22.4 亿元（约合 3.0918 亿美元）的价格出售了深圳一块地块，比近七年前购买同一块 19,000 平方米地块的价格低了 27% 以上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 09:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-sells-shenzhen-land-plot-loss-making-reserve-price-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织总干事谭德塞对最终达成大流行病条约“充满信心”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/who-chief-tedros-confident-eventual-pandemic-treaty-deal-2024-05-27/</link><description>世界卫生组织总干事周一表示，相信各国在上周未能达成协议后有一天能够就流行病协议达成协议，尽管卫生官员警告称这可能需要数年时间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 09:38:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/who-chief-tedros-confident-eventual-pandemic-treaty-deal-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>韩国、中国、日本四年来首次峰会后联合声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-joint-declaration-after-first-summit-four-years-2024-05-27/</link><description>韩国、中国和日本领导人周一发表联合声明，涵盖贸易、气候变化和老龄化社会等一系列领域的合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 08:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-joint-declaration-after-first-summit-four-years-2024-05-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>